      <h1>Jobs at Stripe</h1>
      <p>
        We’re looking for people who care deeply about quality of execution and who want to build technology that people love to&nbsp;use.
      </p>

      <!--<img src="/img/jobs/pictures.png" width="492" height="338" />-->
