    <li>Be highly analytical, love having data to back up an argument, and be a strong believer in knowing the numbers and what they mean.</li>
    <li>Be naturally curious: if something seems off, they’ll figure out what is going on and fix it.</li>
    <li>Think globally, act locally, and thrive in a multicultural, startup environment.</li>
    <li>Like and be willing to travel.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Applying:</h2>
