  </p>

  <ul>
    <li>A description of your relevant background and interests.</li>
    <li>Three paragraphs on how you would scale Stripe in your country. </li>
    <li>A link to relevant online profiles (e.g. LinkedIn, Twitter).</li>
  </ul>

